cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.NE 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing and sentiment analysis. The use of neural networks and recurrent architectures also suggests that it could belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper involves information retrieval and memory mechanisms, which could place it in cs.IR (Information Retrieval) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) sub-categories.
